        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\n(1 comment)\n\nAs is, this code will not work in an execute node.  The execute node can only invoke methods that take Map<String, String>, SvcLogicContext as arguments (in which case it passes a map containing <param> tags  passed in the node in that Map object",
